ZH: 氢弹是一种核武器。
EN: The hydrogen bomb is a type of nuclear weapon.

ZH: 氢弹的爆炸威力非常巨大。
EN: The explosion power of a hydrogen bomb is incredibly immense.

ZH: 在军事中，氢弹被视为一种高级武器。
EN: In military terms, the hydrogen bomb is considered an advanced weapon.

ZH: 氢弹的制造需要高度精密。
EN: The production of a hydrogen bomb requires high precision.

ZH: 氢弹的威胁性不容小觑。
EN: The threat posed by a hydrogen bomb is not to be underestimated.

ZH: 这个国家宣称拥有氢弹技术。
EN: This country claims to possess hydrogen bomb technology.

ZH: 氢弹的使用受到国际禁止。
EN: The use of hydrogen bombs is prohibited internationally.

ZH: 据报道，该国正在进行氢弹试验。
EN: It is reported that the country is conducting hydrogen bomb tests.

ZH: 氢弹的爆炸可以造成巨大的伤亡。
EN: The explosion of a hydrogen bomb can cause massive casualties.

ZH: 防止氢弹落入恐怖组织手中是当务之急。
EN: Preventing hydrogen bombs from falling into the hands of terrorist organizations is a top priority.

ZH: 这个研究机构专注于氢弹技术的发展。
EN: This research institute focuses on the development of hydrogen bomb technology.

ZH: 国际社会普遍谴责氢弹的使用。
EN: The international community widely condemns the use of hydrogen bombs.

ZH: 这个城市曾受到氢弹袭击。
EN: This city was once attacked by a hydrogen bomb.

ZH: 据信，敌对国家正计划使用氢弹打击我国。
EN: It is believed that hostile countries are planning to use hydrogen bombs to attack our country.

ZH: 各国政府正在就禁止氢弹的决议进行谈判。
EN: Governments around the world are negotiating resolutions to ban hydrogen bombs.

ZH: 据报道，该国成功研制出氢弹。
EN: It is reported that the country has successfully developed hydrogen bombs.

ZH: 氢弹技术的发展引起了国际社会的担忧。
EN: The development of hydrogen bomb technology has raised concerns in the international community.

ZH: 这种核武器比传统炸弹更为致命。
EN: This type of nuclear weapon is more deadly than traditional bombs.

ZH: 一场氢弹爆炸将导致大规模破坏。
EN: An explosion of a hydrogen bomb would result in massive destruction.

ZH: 氢弹是当今最强大的武器之一。
EN: The hydrogen bomb is one of the most powerful weapons today.
